reviewText: I liked it so much, a story line and interesting plot. Now, to find volume 1. No matter what people think. It is well made. Sure it's adult theme. What ever roll you socks. I collect them.

The teacher asks Akiyama, a geeky bespectacled boy, and Ieda, a popular jock, to visit Noriko's house because she's been absent from school for some time. Akiyama and Ieda find Noriko, a pretty girl, alone at home. They think Noriko has a bad cold which she can't come to school but really she suffers from being upsess with sex, she talks Akiyama and Ieda into a threesome.
